The evidence with the title 'Remarks by the president on jobs for the Middle Class, 07/30/13 ... ' says Jul 30, 2013  ... Today , our businesses have created 7.2 million new jobs over the last 40 months. This year , we're off to our best private-sector jobs growth since 1999. We now sell more products made in America to the rest of the world than ever before . ( applause.) We produce more renewable energy than ever. 
